### Factory & Execution

```cpp
BehaviorTreeFactory factory;
factory.registerNodeType<MyNode>("MyNode");

auto tree = factory.createTreeFromFile("tree.xml");

while (running) {
    auto status = tree.tickRoot();
    if (status != NodeStatus::RUNNING) break;
    sleep(100ms);
}
```

